<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">有人问：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">家有小胖丫是种什么体验呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那简直是：随时随地想rua。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鼓鼓的肚子，圆圆的脑袋，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就两字：<strong>可爱！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200814/3feb2799f2d042ff98bdfd28cd747337.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/c40ec160230d4651aae4d5e0b9e77511.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在韩国，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有这样一位小朋友</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">靠着自己的肉肉圈了几百万粉丝。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200814/718dfae0de024fe3acf43d322673d91b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">她叫罗熙，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为妈妈偶然间发了她的生活照，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">悄然走红于网络。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200814/0316a1e0db994e5196ef1054e9f4f8a1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">圆圆的小脸蛋萌翻了一票网友，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还被戏称为「屁股脸」。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200814/37907c2b54244c41be5ecf1b0a78ceff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都说女儿像爸，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看了这张全家福，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不得不感慨网友诚不欺我，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>爸爸的基因实在太强大！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200814/98416077cee742ff9a1a9e492de5af26.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我终于找到女儿瘦弱的原因，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想到儿科医生告诉我，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你们两个一米六几，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">100来斤的父母，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想要生一个一米七，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肉嘟嘟的小孩子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">根本不可能！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>生无可恋.jpg</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200814/4d76990420e24b75aaa14d98cabf381a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而我们罗熙的肉肉固然跟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">先天基因分不开，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>同时也靠自己后天的不断努力。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>凭本事长的肉，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>才更健康！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200814/8cc04e0a34bf4eb38010cd4302929317.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我和我的奶瓶🍼，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一刻都不能分割，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无论我走到哪里，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都喝出一首赞歌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200814/1b378cc58ca94e63a878e9108f640791.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">试问这圆嘟嘟的小脸蛋，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁看了不想嗷呜咬一口！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200814/6ac41d290384415487f27996b8e07ef9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这圆滚滚的小身子，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哪位老母亲看了不心痒痒！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200814/0b3a1c4a6e6448fbabdc95b4bc664680.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我不是胖嘟嘟，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我只是肉很多！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200814/fdca3a3be4f54b1089a61f08136798ba.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看了熙熙的照片一大批网友直呼：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又想骗我生女儿！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>小胖丫真的太太太可爱了！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200814/64afbeaf574e4fe6a592f22a92ec21c0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是百万网友自发组成了熙熙后援会，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为她制作表情包。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/802baf8970564fa082057252b1ad88a2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">👇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你笑起来真好看！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">像春天的花一样，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把所有的烦恼所有忧愁，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">统统都吹散！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200814/2e5e431010a8414393572821c672fe34.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200814/1efe7f7fc15f4699a659b3ccba21f481.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">👇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可怜无助弱小，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但能吃！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200814/c89fb00f1326439989e5ebd73c465484.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200814/0fe705d8a9304443846d90103d1a957d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">👇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">敢欺负美女？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我哭给你看！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200814/a6a698c094d6454fbeeac7be53a86d1e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200814/441d0b972ea547daa7c56513cef2841a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">👇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给你一秒钟，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再不回我信息我就生气了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200814/826e9745de3645ecb509a8bce7c4ba61.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200814/49103e2713dc4a5194aba18026ca0f7f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">👇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">跟老公发这个表情包，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百试不爽！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200814/95e0b0ed50d6466a84a64f4595af7dee.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200814/94afabbf7b6e4e2991f143f87280282e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">👇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">皮一下赶紧跑，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">略略略！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200814/bfedac81e820433e887a807563dc7948.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200814/89d08cf2b5e8485f8e1b89d4d4ff5187.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">👇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对不起，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我错了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放过我吧！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/11a73be150fd4f7c8b7430f1096c50a4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200814/a0e4edbf387a41e8beb356280aec4939.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">👇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">快给你的小可爱开门！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/3cbba2e30e184ef9b9a4dda093c38d62.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200814/7853807ac6344f5d8d7308ca2b28001e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不得不说，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们罗熙的表情真的太丰富了，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随手一截都是戏！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200814/b06ac933541f47c4a945f39787cb15c0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也有不少网友担心，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哎，小孩子确实是肉多点可爱，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200814/321e843664e244b7bea936903ab4b6b1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可我们熙熙那么像爸爸，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>长大可怎么办呢！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200814/7c48e1b264584e13bbfffb3ed0983c56.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但是，没想到，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们熙熙越长大，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>爸爸的显性基因逐渐失效，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>妈妈的隐性基因开始持续发力！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200814/09527fbd51fb46648bb7cafc5cf88c4e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妈妈给熙熙留起了长发，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200814/c73d476531b84e2d84aa068d7eb4f8f0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两个可爱的小辫子，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">配上圆滚滚的脑袋，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要多萌有多萌！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200814/71d79e66dac347ca8502d32144b8d8e0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为妈妈做儿童服装生意，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">熙熙就帮妈妈当起了网店的童装模特。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/361d45c6a1f64279a92e4c317bfcca69.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">穿上美丽的小裙子，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200814/30208a066da74d97ad7e08d476d4f569.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">戴上摩登的墨镜，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200814/a9862c2c964e493b9c6666514b83ca36.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">简直就是这条街最靓的崽！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200814/65a248060aae405694b9ae92808600d7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至还和妈妈留起了母女bobo头，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就更像了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200814/5a2564667d83451f9874b00590bf9eca.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">写到这里，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看着我女儿神似他爸爸的单眼皮眼睛，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">突然对未来充满了无限希望，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>女大十八变，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一定能比爹好看！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/e60ef3f53ef94616969f550d6fb7f9f5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200814/d9d6415e30384711950c47f3cbed1639.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然才4岁，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但我们熙熙凭着自己古灵精怪的表情包，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200814/3c7b68d18f1e49b1947c50218db3bb5e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200814/1632626b0f124046ad717ee7f5c7ac21.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以及绝佳的时尚品味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和傲人的美貌，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200814/a71e4dbdae104b3090760e2677ba6209.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200814/78f4ae589f3a4137a7f7ec7cc6321470.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一跃成为韩国「国民女儿」，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刷爆ins，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赶超宋民国，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>成为表情包之首！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>真是美滋滋！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200814/e1d3376ba3d04366990541efce191db9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">网友甚至还喊话熙熙：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>胖嘟嘟很可爱！千万别减肥！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200814/e8d47dc860d645188b1c2044266e43f2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">与此同时，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们熙熙也多了一个可爱的妹妹，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">叫「糕糕」！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200814/8c20264205984b6489536228acdde9e8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有同样肉嘟嘟的「屁股脸」，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比熙熙更像爸爸嗷！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200814/6bbb6600097a463a9129963b68dd0adc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200814/7f9f8915dbf845468279e7c2c5d3a33d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">熙熙小小年纪，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就开始学习承受</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个年纪不该承受的重量：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>看二胎！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200814/d8332fa2c4fd4a3a81c105d90b7c73e0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一起吃饭：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200814/a1ee5142b4974ca796aa9f71350b62c3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一起睡觉：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200814/c68cd0edf5614756a7fd380103ca794b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一起洗澡：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至带妹妹去上学：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200814/b69eaf9764ec4d999fe8e2a920f6c2e5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以说，从妹妹在妈妈肚子里，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">熙熙都陪在她身边，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>见证着妹妹从一个小不点，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>慢慢长大。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200814/cf91121930964ec7a8cb9c2025b45e47.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一起学习，也一起成长，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">会打打闹闹，也能说说笑笑。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200814/d0a3372bf88c471cb0a88c16dd762641.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">她们春天去郊游，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200814/d36ff30af8ba4d50b880eb8436105088.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夏天去野餐；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200814/cf0f4e781e5e462bb4cc50de0045087d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
